title: Error in final step of installation
body_html:
Following the instructions at http://tensorflow.org/get_started/os_setup.md#virtualenv_install

The last command for installation is this --
"(tensorflow)unknownb8e85638de86:tensorflow jonathanmalkin$ pip install --upgrade <$url_to_binary.whl>"

I get the following response --
"-bash: syntax error near unexpected token `newline'"
